Reports an assignment that is used as the condition of an <code>if</code>, <code>while</code>, <code>for</code>, or
<code>do</code> statement. Although occasionally intended,
this usage is confusing, and often indicates a typo
(for example, <code>=</code> instead of <code>==</code>).
